latestPosts.caption:
Ending 2024 on a high note! 
Being at the Cosmo Bloggers Award for the Lifestyle Influencer East category has to be the highlight of the year for me. The day was filled with creativity, glamour, and inspiring conversations with incredible people from all over India- definitely one for the books! 💫

This year has been about taking things one step at a time and learning as I go. I’m not going to lie, I’m super proud of myself for having the courage to make a major career shift and step into the public eye, fully putting myself out there. It’s been a year of being fearless, determined, and passionate about following my dreams, and this is one of those moments that I truly felt proud of my journey and how far I’ve come.

Here’s to 2025- onwards and upwards to bigger and better things ✨💖

@cosmoindia @lovecolorbar

Earrings: @amamajewels 
Hair and make up: @makeupby_vikvinartistry

Let this be the tune that plays in your head every time you think it’s too late to start.

It’s never too late. You’re not too old. You haven’t missed the boat.
Dreams don’t come with an expiry date.
I changed my career at 35- and couldn’t be happier. If I had waited, I’d have missed this version of my life.
This is my mantra. Let it be yours too:
You can start at any age.
Repeat it. Believe it. Let it sink in.
Share this with someone who needs to hear it. 💫🔥
